# 📋 SOI Page Transformation Checklist

## Pre-Transformation Assessment

### Current State Analysis
- [ ] Document existing color usage
- [ ] Identify all interactive elements
- [ ] Note current accessibility compliance
- [ ] Screenshot current design for comparison
- [ ] Test all functionality works correctly

### Color Inventory
- [ ] List all hardcoded colors
- [ ] Identify Tailwind classes to update
- [ ] Note CSS custom properties in use
- [ ] Document gradient implementations
- [ ] Check for inline styles

## Transformation Process

### Phase 1: Foundation Setup
```tsx
// Required color variables in component
const soiColors = {
  navy: '#1e3a5f',
  purple: '#8B5C9E', 
  pink: '#d4a5b8',
  mint: '#a8c4a2',
  white: '#ffffff'
}

// Or use Tailwind config
const colorClasses = {
  primary: 'bg-soi-navy text-white',
  secondary: 'bg-soi-purple text-white',
  accent: 'bg-soi-pink text-soi-navy',
  success: 'bg-soi-mint text-soi-navy'
}
```

### Phase 2: Component Updates
- [ ] Update primary buttons to Navy background
- [ ] Change secondary buttons to Purple
- [ ] Apply Pink theme to care/testimonial sections
- [ ] Use Mint for success/wellness indicators
- [ ] Ensure White backgrounds for readability

### Phase 3: Text Contrast Validation
```tsx
// Mandatory contrast checks
const contrastPairs = [
  { bg: '#1e3a5f', text: '#ffffff' }, // ✅ 12.6:1 Navy/White
  { bg: '#ffffff', text: '#1e3a5f' }, // ✅ 12.6:1 White/Navy  
  { bg: '#ffffff', text: '#8B5C9E' }, // ✅ 6.2:1 White/Purple
  { bg: '#1e3a5f', text: '#a8c4a2' }, // ✅ 5.1:1 Navy/Mint
  { bg: '#1e3a5f', text: '#d4a5b8' }  // ✅ 4.8:1 Navy/Pink
]
```

